Michael,<br><br>
I am glad to see you post here. I sometimes do not know who is in control, me or the PTSD. I do now recognize it, and I am determined to win. I have feelings for which I still do not have names, but there are real feelings surfacing, or so I believe. The emptiness still pokes me every so often, just to let me know it is still there. <br><br>
It sounds to me like you are determined to win too!<br><br>
We all have to hang tough!
